Les_etapes_dune_creation_de_site_multilingue\" >Les \u00e9tapes d&#8217;une cr\u00e9ation de site multilingue<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/comment-creer-un-site-multilingue\/#1_Evaluation_et_planification\" >1. Evaluation et planification<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/comment-creer-un-site-multilingue\/#2_Selection_dun_CMS_adapte\" >2. S\u00e9lection d&#8217;un CMS adapt\u00e9<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/comment-creer-un-site-multilingue\/#3_Traduction_et_adaptation_des_contenus\" >3. Traduction et adaptation des contenus<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/comment-creer-un-site-multilingue\/#4_Conception_UXUI\" >4. Conception UX\/UI<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/comment-creer-un-site-multilingue\/#5_Mise_en_place_dun_systeme_de_commutation_de_langue\" >5. Mise en place d&#8217;un syst\u00e8me de commutation de langue<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/comment-creer-un-site-multilingue\/#6_Optimisation_SEO_pour_chaque_langue\" >6. Optimisation SEO pour chaque langue<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-l